---
title: Lemony Chickpea Salad with Prosciutto with Honey Dijon Dressing, Parmesan & Sunflower Seeds
description: This hearty salad is all you need for a light-yet-satisfying lunch. You’ll toss crisp lettuce in a lemony honey-Dijon dressing spiked with as many chili flakes as you like (or none at all—you’re the chef!). You’ll add tender chickpeas and crunchy sunflower seeds, and top with two of our very favorite salad add-ons: savory-salty prosciutto and crisp croutons.
